mutual interest to both countries and a forceful impetus to
stability and peace in the Balkans,'' Bulatovic was quoted as
saying to Milosevic.
	   For Borislav, brother of Slobodan and former representative in a
chamber of commerce, this is the first posting in diplomacy.
