w2094 &Cx1f; wstm-
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-Opener Advisory   10-12 0078
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-Opener, Advisory,0077 </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
EDITORS:
</HEADLINE>

<TEXT>
	   The Associated Press closes its news cycle for Monday, Oct. 12,
1998, and begins its report for Tuesday, Oct. 13.
