<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-FEA-US-Shoppers' Paradise-Price Box,0340 </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
With FEA-US-Shoppers' Paradise
</HEADLINE>
 &UR; By The Associated Press &QC; 

<TEXT>
	   A list of consumer prices around the world. In most cases prices
listed are those at department or electronics stores. Designer
brands are excluded, unless otherwise specified.
	   Sony digital camera: 100,000 yen (dlrs 854) in Tokyo; 1,150,000
lire (dlrs 709) in Rome; from dlrs 499 in New York. At some
electronics stores in New York, visitors who pay cash can get a
lower rate than the sticker price.
	   ___
	   Designer leather handbag: 50,000 to 100,000 yen (dlrs 427 to
dlrs 854) in Tokyo; from dlrs 120 in New York;
	   ___
