	   TOKYO (AP) _ The U.S. dollar was trading at 117.90 yen on the
Tokyo foreign exchange market at 9 a.m. (0000 GMT) Tuesday, up 1.18
yen from its level of 116.72 yen as of 5 p.m. (0800 GMT) Monday.
