NATO: WRAP 2 - NATO has finalised plans for airstrikes against
Yugoslavia, possibly as early as the coming weekend. APTN has the
announcement by NATO chief Javier Solana plus coverage of US envoy
Richard Holbrooke meeting officials from NATO and OSCE to brief them
on his talks with Yugoslav President Slobodan Milosevic. The package
includes a number of comments by Holbrooke. (WRAP FIRST RUNS 0300
EUROPE)
