military air strikes at Serbia for four days to allow time for
international inspectors to verify that Yugoslavia had fully met its
commitments on withdrawing forces from Kosovo and initiating peace
negotiations. (RUSHES RUN 0050 LIVE/CUTSPOT FOR 0300 EUROPE)
